Package: rforcpue
Title: Functions to Assist With The Analysis of CPUE Data
Description: General functions to assist with CPUE standardization. 
    They include functions to conduct simple linear models, GLMs,
    and GAMs, with examples to assist people in their use.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
